/* PROC REPORT: */

/* SYNTAX--> */
/* PROC REPORT DATA=TABLE_NAME OUT=TABLE_NAME; */
/* COLUMNS<COLUM1><COLUM2><COLUM2>...    LIST ALL THE COLUMNS WHICH HAS TO BE USED IN PROC REPORT */
/* DEFINE COLUMN_NAME/ACTION;          DESCRIBE/ASSIGN ACTION TO EACH OF THE VARIABLES TO BE USED IN PROC REPORT */
/* BREAK COLUMN_NAME/ACTION;           SEPARATE ONE SEGMENT FROM ANOTHER OR SUMMARIZE BY SEGMENT, EG:- SUBTOTAL */
/* RBREAK COLUMN_NAME/ACTION;          SUMMARIZE AT THE BOTTOM, EG:- GRAND TOTAL */
/* COMPUTE VAR; */
/* 		LOGICS HERE;                   CONDITIONALLY CREATE NEW COLUMNS, DEFINE FORMAT OR OTHER ACTIONS */
/* ENDCOMP; */
/* RUN; */


